node.text: We just had an 80lb blacktip shark bust our terminal tackle. Can you name another species of fish that weighs 80lbs that can destroy terminal tackle like this with around 10lbs of drag? #blacktiph #fishing #terminaltackle #tackle #busted #hook #rig #blacktip #blacktipshark #surffishing

node.text: In this video, I go fishing with Florida Fish and Wildlife Conservation Commission on Lake Weohyakapka using electricity to catch giant fish! Our goal was to find a 10lb bass. We caught a monster 10lb and 12lb bass!!

node.title: Using ELECTRICITY to Catch GIANT Fish

node.text: I got a phone call from the @brooklynfishingclub about an insane bluefin tuna bite within miles of New York City. We changed all of our plans last minute and managed to get to Brooklyn to meet up with Victor and @rockfishcharters. By the time we stepped on the boat, we had been going for nearly 30 hours straight with zero sleep. Once we got a few miles off the city, we could see the bluefin tuna feeding on the surface. @delphfishing and I brought up the kite fishing gear to try some South Florida kite fishing techniques on these bluefin tuna. After a few minutes, bluefin tuna started airing out in the kite! In total, we hooked five bluefin tuna and landed three. On the way back to the dock, we decided to stop by the Statue of Liberty to try striped bass fishing. Unfortunately, the current was too strong, but we did manage to get some incredible photos of the bluefin tuna we kept by the Statue of Liberty #blacktiph #fishing #newyork #nyc #newyorkcity #statueofliberty #bluefin #bluefintuna #tunafishing #epic #saltwaterfishing 📸 @davis_bennett_

node.text: We just launched our BlacktipH Platinum Club for our most dedicated fans! We will be uploading exclusive content to the Platinum Club that won’t be see on any other platform. Also will be giving away monthly fishing trips to members, merch discounts, and much more! Click the link in our bio for more details! #blacktiph

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BlacktipH in YouTube with @youtube, and @blacktiphbrand. May be an image of text that says 'BILLION VIEWS'.

node.text: We just hit 1 billion views on YouTube!! 🙌 This is an incredible milestone for a fishing show! If you told me back in 2006, when I began uploading, that we would one day reach a billion views, I wouldn't believe you! Thank you for all the support! #blacktiph #fishingshow #youtube #milestone @blacktiphbrand

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BlacktipH in Cypress Cove Marina & Lodge with @yesjulz, @d_riley40, @louisthornton22, @jakejorgs, @tidelineboats, and @blacktiphbrand. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: My brother @jakejorgs caught his first swordfish with @d_riley40 and @louisthornton22 #blacktiph #swordfish #swordfishing #louisiana #louisianafishing #saltwaterfishing #oceanfishing 📸 @davis_bennett_
These are some of the most insane shark moments we’ve filmed over the years #blacktiph #fishing #shark #sharks #sharkattack #sharkfishing #aerialphotography #drone #florida #bahamas #sharkweek
